{"tid":2339148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京施壓 蘋果在中國將刪除數千款遊戲app","createTime":"2020-12-24T12:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T12:26:07.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32207231bec1fc8378a2655dfc8efb5dccf2d5bb","tid":2339148,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"2016年中國曾宣布要求遊戲app需要獲得監管機關的許可，但在蘋果的app store可以規避此一要求，然而好景不常，外媒透露，蘋果將因應中國政府要求，把數千款遊戲app下架。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報導，蘋果公司年初已在中國的平台撤下數千款app，根據一份備忘錄顯示，蘋果本月警告中國遊戲開發商，在新一波行動中，遊戲app將成為目標，可能會從app store中撤除。<br />\n<br />\n4年前中國政府開始要求遊戲app必須取得許可，但開發商能在蘋果的app store中規避這項要求，蘋果沒有解釋為何存在此漏洞，也沒有說明今年為何關閉漏洞，國外遊戲開發商對此感到遺憾，因為在中國，遊戲獲得批准有其難度。報導指出，中國監管機關未對此做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3390591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390591&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=48887dc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390591&h=7d03d52b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3390591</a><br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/apples-china-app-store-sheds-games-under-pressure-11608719400?mod=searchresults_pos3&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fapples-china-app-store-sheds-games-under-pressure-11608719400%3Fmod%3Dsearchresults_pos3%26page%3D1&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=91b51993\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/apples-china-app-store-sheds-games-under-pressure-11608719400?mod=searchresults_pos3&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"5958149d4b469e556f598e669ba82e3ddc11a304","tid":2339148,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"淪落到只可以用華為"}]}